Or have a foot pedal to actuate the lock. No monkey (in insti) is tall
enough to put a foot on the ground and open the door at the same time.

On Sep 26, 2016 6:07 PM, "Lazim Kainikkara" <lazimk100@gmail.com wrote:

 spring hinge with a lever/initial push switch. i mean the door can be only
 opened only when the lever/switch is engaged for the instance. after
 opening the switch can be released (kind of switch we see on suitcase ,
 with spring).. and after filling bottle door closes with spring mechanism
 and held tight with the switch.
 i think monkey cant engage the lever and lift door simultaneosly

