 Hello gangasters,
 Monkeys have been tasting/testing our water dispensers for a long time,
 mainly because we don't close the cage / small monkeys get inside the
 dispenser through the opening in the front door. My suggestion is to put a
 spring hinge, to close the doors automatically, and also to permanently
 close the opening in the front door.

 @gensec Can this be implemented?
 @gangasters Is there a better/cheaper alternative for this?

 
